Rampa com boa área para decolagem, e com muitos locais para pouso a frente da rampa. Para chegar a rampa saindo de Mauriti - CE, siga pela Avenida Doutor Fernandes Teles Cartaxo em direção a Rua Rosendo Neco de Souza, km 2, nesse ponto siga a pé em direção a rampa, em uma subida acentuada de aproximadamente 130 metros. waypoint.name: Il Nudo
waypoint.description: Il Nudo, you should take the navetta (van) from the Delta Club Laveno, because there is a locked gate on the way to the ramp, (unless you´re willing to carry the glider on your shoulders for 30 minutes). From the point where the Navetta drops you, you still have to carry the glider on your shoulders upward for 5 minutes. It´s a natural ramp, grassy, with medium incline, with a somewhat restricted setup area, you might have to set up behind the ramp on a very steep grassy incline. Any winds from the South are usually good. If there´s very little wind it might be a marginal take off for hang gliders because there´s not much of a vertical drop in front, if any, so you might have to run a lot, and clear the trees. Be wary. But with any sustainable wind, it´s a classic natural launch.
